Package: mapMementoR
Title: Create Aesthetic Race Route or Hiking Maps from GPX Tracks and performance data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Black", email = "ben.black812@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for parsing GPX files, extracting race route data, and generating aesthetic maps with OpenStreetMap backgrounds, elevation charts, and customizable styles. Includes batch processing and Powerof10 integration for athlete data.
